## 5. Empty State → Configured State → In Progress → Ready

### Empty State (nuevo proyecto, nada ingresado):

```
  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  Start by identifying the material            │
  │                                               │
  │  Material Family *        [Select         ▾]  │
  │                                               │
  │  Selecting a material type configures this    │
  │  workspace for the data that matters.         │
  │                                               │
  │  Or start with notes from a call:             │
  │  [Voice Note]  [Paste Notes]  [Upload Doc]    │
  │                                               │
  │  Core fields (always collected):              │
  │  Material Name      [_____________________]   │
  │  Generating Process  [____________________]   │
  │  Physical State     [Select             ▾]    │
  │  Form / Packaging   [Select tags         ]    │
  │  Volume             [________] [unit    ▾]    │
  │  Recurrence         [Select             ▾]    │
  │  Urgency            [Select             ▾]    │
  │  Production Critical [Select            ▾]    │
  └──────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### Readiness Banner (cuando el umbral se cumple):

```
  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  ✓ Ready to generate proposal                 │
  │  72% complete · 0 critical blockers            │
  │  2 optional suggestions pending                │
  │                                [Generate →]   │
  └──────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

